OL,3,CPolice investigating whether stabbing
OL,4,Cand shooting in south London are linked
OL,6,FPolice are investigating the
OL,7,Fpossibility that the stabbing of a man
OL,8,Fand the shooting of four people in the
OL,9,Fsame area of south London are linked.
OL,11,FMetropolitan Police officers were
OL,12,Fcalled at 1.14am on Saturday to
OL,13,Freports of shots fired from a vehicle
OL,14,Fin Coldharbour Lane, Brixton, and at
OL,15,F2.17am to reports of a stabbing in
OL,16,Fnearby Acre Lane.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
