CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777914346
OL,3,CPolice investigating whether stabbing
OL,4,Cand shooting in south London are linked
OL,6,FFour people were taken to hospital
OL,7,Fwith gunshot wounds following the
OL,8,FColdharbour Lane incident, including a
OL,9,F25-year-old man who remains in a life-
OL,10,Fthreatening condition.
OL,12,FThree others ` aged 21, 47 and 70 `
OL,13,Fwere also taken to hospital with
OL,14,Finjuries assessed as not life
OL,15,Fthreatening or life changing.
OL,17,FSome 700 metres away in Acre Lane, a
OL,18,F33-year-old man was found with
OL,19,Fmultiple stab wounds and taken to
OL,20,Fhospital where he remains in a life-
OL,21,Fthreatening condition.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
