OL,3,CPolice investigating whether stabbing
OL,4,Cand shooting in south London are linked
OL,6,FNo arrests have been made yet in
OL,7,Fconnection with either event.
OL,9,FOfficers are investigating the
OL,10,Fpossibility that the two incidents are
OL,11,Flinked, the Met said.
OL,13,FAnyone with information or footage is
OL,14,Furged to contact the police or
OL,15,FCrimestoppers quoting reference CAD
OL,16,F557/2May for the Coldharbour Lane
OL,17,Fshooting and quoting CAD 907/2May for
OL,18,Fthe Acre Lane stabbing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
