OL,3,CPolice investigating whether stabbing
OL,4,Cand shooting in south London are linked
OL,6,FSeveral police officers could be seen
OL,7,Fsearching an area of grass outside the
OL,8,FSouthwyck House estate, on Coldharbour
OL,9,FLane, on Saturday evening.
OL,11,FAn estate resident said he believed
OL,12,Fthe incident took place during a
OL,13,Fbarbecue party on the patch of green,
OL,14,Fwhile a shop worker told of providing
OL,15,Fshelter to people in the wake of
OL,16,Fgunshots.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
