OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777914346
OL,3,CPolice investigating whether stabbing
OL,4,Cand shooting in south London are linked
OL,6,FMoh John, 45, who works at supermarket
OL,7,FPayless Food & Wine outside Southwyck
OL,8,FHouse estate, told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "I was putting something
OL,10,Fthere and I heard the noises.
OL,12,F"It was busy, there was a party. I saw
OL,13,Fthe people run away.
OL,15,F"But then I saw the people, some
OL,16,Fpeople try to come in the shop and I
OL,17,Flocked the door."
OL,26,@qD@NOUtD@AOUwD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
