OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777914346
OL,3,CPolice investigating whether stabbing
OL,4,Cand shooting in south London are linked
OL,6,FHe said those rushing inside the
OL,7,Fsupermarket were "scared", adding he
OL,8,Fkept the front door locked for "some
OL,9,Ftime" before he reopened it."
OL,11,FRobert, 40, who did not want to give
OL,12,Fhis surname, said he did not see the
OL,13,Fincident as he was inside all night
OL,14,Fbut told PA: "I think it happened at
OL,15,Fthe barbecue. It was packed.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@YO]pD@`OUqD@EO]qD@]O]vD@NOU
