OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777914346
OL,3,CPolice investigating whether stabbing
OL,4,Cand shooting in south London are linked
OL,6,F"I usually feel safe around here,
OL,7,Fpeople know each other and get on.
OL,8,FThere's been a few stabbings, and one
OL,9,Fday one gun was caught, but I don't
OL,10,Fthink anyone's ever been shot like
OL,11,Fthis."
